<div class="about-page">
    <h1>About the Online Democratic Community (ODC)</h1>
    
    <div class="intro-section">
        <h2>A New Model for Community Ownership</h2>
        <p>The ODC is a democratic platform where <strong>you</strong> control how your data is used and how community resources are allocated. Unlike traditional platforms that profit from your data, we're building a community-owned cooperative that puts wellbeing first.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="vision-section">
        <h3>Our Vision: Your Data, Your Choice, Your Community</h3>
        <div class="vision-grid">
            <div class="vision-item">
                <h4>üó≥Ô∏è Democratic Control</h4>
