    </div>

    <div class="how-section">
        <h3>How the ODC Works</h3>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Join the Community</strong> - Create an account and become a voting member</li>
            <li><strong>Participate in Decisions</strong> - Vote on initiatives, budgets, and community rules</li>
            <li><strong>Contribute (Optional)</strong> - Donate funds, share feedback with ethical partners, or help moderate</li>
            <li><strong>Shape Our Future</strong> - Your participation gives you more influence in community decisions</li>
            <li><strong>Benefit Together</strong> - All proceeds fund community-chosen wellbeing initiatives</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="funding-section">
        <h3>How We're Funded</h3>
        <p>The ODC operates on a sustainable, transparent model:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Member Donations</strong> - Like Wikipedia, members who can contribute help support the platform</li>
            <li><strong>Ethical Partnerships</strong> - When companies want community feedback, members can voluntarily participate and proceeds go to the community fund</li>
            <li><strong>No Hidden Data Mining</strong> - We will NEVER sell your data without your explicit consent</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="different-section">
        <h3>Why We're Different</h3>
