                    <li>Extract value from your data</li>
                    <li>Decisions made by executives</li>
                    <li>Profits go to shareholders</li>
                    <li>Opaque algorithms and policies</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="comparison-column odc">
                <h4>Online Democratic Community</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>You control your data</li>
                    <li>Decisions made by community vote</li>
                    <li>All proceeds fund community wellbeing</li>
                    <li>Transparent governance and funding</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="join-section">
